{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_9", "eventName": "風暴瞭望", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "9-4", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "暗火四起", "storyInfo": "風笛前往街道繼續調查，發現當地塔拉人與駐軍矛盾甚深。號角爭取到了與駐軍上校會面的機會。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“當風掀起金色的麥浪”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“野林和管道一齊叮叮噹噹地響”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我在地塊邊緣找到了我的摯愛，緊跟著從天而降的火光”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來這首歌的後半段是這樣唱的......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好悲傷。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "達米安也走了，他甚至都沒法得到一場像樣的葬禮......", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們不可能把他還給我們。他們只會把他燒成灰，隨隨便便地撒向城外，就像對待一捧毫無意義的泥土。", "name": "憤怒的男性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（低聲啜泣）", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先是洛瑞，然後是克里斯，現在他們同樣沒放過達米安。格蘭妮，肖恩被抓走的時候，他們都說他得了礦石病——", "name": "憤怒的男性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不要再說下去了，羅南。肖恩他......他就是不小心得了病。", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他是個勤勞、忠貞的可憐人，唯一的念想就是讓我們母子過上好一點的日子......", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蘭妮，你還沒弄明白嗎？", "name": "憤怒的男性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們就是一顆顆鉚釘。如果生銹了，他們當然會毫不在意地把我們丟棄。", "name": "憤怒的男性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可即便沒有生銹，只要對這座城市機器來說不那麼合適了，我們唯一能等來的也是同樣的命運。", "name": "憤怒的男性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們從來不管我們是不是正在一批批地染上礦石病。", "name": "憤怒的男性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "廠裡每個月發的藥，別的工人能拿到全部，我們就往往只有一半，甚至三分之一。", "name": "憤怒的男性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有防護服。肖恩的防護服穿了多久了？五年，還是七年？你在半夜偷偷替他補過多少回？", "name": "憤怒的男性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有的法案，所有的標準，都只對他們有利。而我們呢？", "name": "憤怒的男性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只配吃他們不想要的馬鈴薯和爛蘋果，哪怕每一寸農用地塊上都浸透了我們的汗水。", "name": "憤怒的男性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只配在工廠裡沒日沒夜地消耗性命，等幹不動了就如他們所願，一個個地全都染病！", "name": "憤怒的男性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣的話，他們就可以順理成章地把我們這些塔拉人全部從自己的城市裡丟出去——", "name": "憤怒的男性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......停下吧，求你。羅南，你的這些話並不能帶來任何好結果。", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看看站在那邊的克萊娜她們。她們正在為自己的兒子和兄長哭泣。你還想讓你們的憤怒給多少人帶來失去摯愛的痛苦？", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這痛苦是殺人犯帶來的。他們在一個接一個地殺死我們，有時用疾病，有時用炮彈。格蘭妮，你不要再欺騙自己。", "name": "憤怒的男性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（壓低聲音）今天早上有好幾個人來找我。奧布萊恩一家，還有康納家的兄弟，他們都決定加入我們了。", "name": "憤怒的男性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你和孩子過得不容易，我們都理解，在這個節骨眼上，我們更需要互相幫助......", "name": "憤怒的男性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......離我和孩子遠一些吧，羅南，看在過去肖恩待你們都還不錯的份上。", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "憤怒的男性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我必須走了，格蘭妮。你看到那邊的人了嗎？她穿著那身制服。", "name": "憤怒的男性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道我們的規矩。我相信你，也請你更信我一些。要是你考慮好了，你可以告訴西爾莎。", "name": "憤怒的男性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃......你好。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請問你認識巴里，呃，達米安·巴里的家人嗎？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（搖頭）", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛才聽到你們唱歌了，我沒有找錯地方啊。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我不知道您想找什麼，但是達米安的母親和姐妹什麼都不知道。", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那他有沒有關係特別好的朋友，或者一起在倉庫工作的人？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我們什麼都不知道......真的......", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.8, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚......求您！您別抓我......", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？抱歉......是我靠太近了嗎？我沒有傷害你們的打算。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好像很怕我。我臉上有什麼東西嗎？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什、什麼都沒有......", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果您允許的話，我得回家了，今早的水果還剩下許多，放著不管的話，它們會很快腐爛......", "name": "悲傷的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_243", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_238"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "凱利上尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_238"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦？那是......凱利上尉？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_238"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克萊娜，我只想看你一眼，我想知道你和菲奧娜還好不好......", "name": "凱利上尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_238"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，是我的錯，但——", "name": "凱利上尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_238"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我沒有辦法。", "name": "凱利上尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_238"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當然記得，我記得全部。達米安他......他是我的外甥。", "name": "凱利上尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_238"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從小看著他長大。我從半島郡調回小丘郡的那天，他親手把酢漿草放在了我的帽子上。", "name": "凱利上尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_238"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他那時候還那麼小......我......", "name": "凱利上尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_238"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......對不起，我不該對著你們說這些。", "name": "凱利上尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_238"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說的對......我什麼都沒做好，我沒臉回到這裡。", "name": "凱利上尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_238"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "達米安和那群人扯上關係，我沒來得及勸阻他......上校的命令我也沒法違抗。", "name": "凱利上尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_238"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，我必須這麼做。這都是為了小丘郡。", "name": "凱利上尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_238"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我愛你們，我也愛這座城市......我不能眼睜睜看著那群人將我們的家扯得四分五裂。", "name": "凱利上尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_238"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我都明白，克萊娜，我的姐妹，我並不是在請求你的原諒。", "name": "凱利上尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_238"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那我......我走了。你......你和菲奧娜一定要好好照顧自己。", "name": "凱利上尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_238"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明天再抽空來看你們......", "name": "凱利上尉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_238"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_238", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "